      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready to get you where you need to go? This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone who appreciates a solid runner and doesn't mind a bit of character! While it shows clear signs of its journey through some cosmetic wear and will benefit from some upcoming routine maintenance, it remains a dependable choice that still has plenty of life left in it. It\u2019s the perfect, budget-friendly option for anyone looking for a functional vehicle with a lot of potential!",
      "price": 19500.0,
