    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that remains in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a deep, mirror-like exterior finish completely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seating remains supple and taut without a single crease, and the original carpets have been protected since day one. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with factory-level precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of service records documenting a 'no-expense-spared' maintenance philosophy. With its pristine engine bay and spotless undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own an investment-quality example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 44900.0,
